== Events == * {{ill|Tenchō|ja|治承|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 4th year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1180|ja|1180|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 10|ja|11月10日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – A historic meeting took place in which brothers {{ill|Minamoto no Yoritomo|ja|源頼朝|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} and {{ill|Minamoto no Yoshiie|ja|源義経|lt=Yoshiie?|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (the text reads “実朝” but context suggests a name change) met for the first time on the banks of the Kise River in Suruga. * {{ill|Seiwa|ja|貞和|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year/{{ill|Kōkoku|ja|興国|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 6th year（{{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1345|ja|1345|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 15|ja|11月15日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – The Northern Court changed its era name from {{ill|Kangyō|ja|康永|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} to {{ill|Teiwa|ja|貞和|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} . * {{ill|Kansei|ja|Kansei|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 12nd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1800|ja|1800|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|December 7|ja|12月7日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Inō Tadataka|ja|Ino Tadataka|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} finished surveying Ezo and the Ōshū Kaidō and returned to Edo, presenting his draft map to the shogunate in December. * {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 4th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1857|ja|1857|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|December 7|ja|12月7日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – U.S. Consul {{ill|Townsend Harris|ja|ハリス|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} visited Edo Castle and met with {{ill|Tokugawa Iesada|ja|徳川家定|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} .
== Births == * {{ill|Genwa (Japan)|ja|元和|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 3rd year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1617|ja|1617|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 21|ja|11月21日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Tosa Mitsuki|ja|土佐光起|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , a painter († {{ill|1691|ja|1691|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
* {{ill|Hōreki|ja|Hōreki|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 10th year（{{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|1760|ja|1760|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} {{ill|November 30|ja|11月30日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ） – {{ill|Kawaoka Seishū|ja|華岡青洲|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , a physician and pioneer of anesthesia († {{ill|1835|ja|1835|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ).
